data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER!! ORIGINAL OWNERS!! Wonderful 3 bed 2 bath single family corner lot in cul-de-sac in the quiet community of Boynton Lakes.  Enclosed 4th room can be used as a home office. House was recently painted with new roof installed in 2013. AC 2018. W/H 1999. Large oversized driveway. 2-car garage. Close to great schools, parks, shopping, restaurants and quick access to I-95. **Schedule SHOWINGS through SHOWING TIME.
